         <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#RDS">
            <p>When Theon was in office...Pantime, daughter of Lykiskos...buys five houses...Phinton, son of Lykiskos, guardian...Sosias, Philonidas...Herakleidas, Antallos...</p>
         </div>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>The engraving of this brief contract is extremely light and difficult to read. The list of names at the end, headed by the brother of the buyer (who is designated as the "guardian" of his sister, who could not transact business independently), likely comprises the guarantors of the contract.</p>
         </div>
